{"tid":1231343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暫緩修例】星島：林鄭昨晤建制派　麥美娟不滿表現激動　葉劉中途離場","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T09:00:52.000Z","uid":156868,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"21b5668790822af4899b795032fb465177290bdd","tid":1231343,"uid":156868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%98%A8%E6%99%A4%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE-%E9%BA%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%A8%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%94%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4/?fbclid=IwAR2vqX0GHkBpPzRM6CUr6RblGmqxpHJbVuJZzDcvuwR2FfwQ61G-0f-2TmY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2598%25A8%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A8%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2580%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2vqX0GHkBpPzRM6CUr6RblGmqxpHJbVuJZzDcvuwR2FfwQ61G-0f-2TmY&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=1718d3fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2598%25A8%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A8%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2580%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2vqX0GHkBpPzRM6CUr6RblGmqxpHJbVuJZzDcvuwR2FfwQ61G-0f-2TmY&h=997f2719\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%98%A8%E6%99%A4%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE-%E9%BA%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%A8%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%94%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4/?fbclid=IwAR2vqX0GHkBpPzRM6CUr6RblGmqxpHJbVuJZzDcvuwR2FfwQ61G-0f-2TmY</a><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨日宣布暫緩修例，她昨日公布前先與建制派議員會面，交代決定。《明報》、《星島日報》、now 新聞等報道，林鄭月娥在席上多次向他們致歉，又形容自己提出修例惹反響似「撼頭埋牆」。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報道，她在禮賓府先行接見全國政協副主席董建華會面，之後分別與全體行政會議成員、立法會建制派議員，及下午與民主派議員會面，交代暫緩決定及作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，多名建制議員認為林鄭不應暫緩，而且「轉軚」令支持修例議員難以向支持者交代，擔心今明兩年的區議會及立法會選舉選情，當中工聯會議員反應較大，麥美娟更激動地表達不滿，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀半途離場。now 新聞報道，林鄭昨日與建制派會面，有地區直選議員落淚。"},{"pid":"cd3d06321b254dab4ea8b0bef8df605f034957c3","tid":1231343,"uid":196924,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，呢頭撐你嗰頭暫緩，我地下屆點撚樣選呀？你唔洗向選民交代，我地要架！(設計對白)"},{"pid":"8e04216bb4e86356aae72cc2aa53f8e26acaa6fa","tid":1231343,"uid":51753,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"諗起掃把頭起身走人個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6683279806d293246f3ad52ea650e787f70fbced","tid":1231343,"uid":32722,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"麥美娟一向頭腦簡單，正豬閪。<br />\n呢種人都上到位係工聯會之恥"},{"pid":"e3ae7a069eaceca71e329b8535dd33589aeddbd5","tid":1231343,"uid":31744,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:55:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭 建制 disconnected<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bf6edd02a141eac99bcf417ae4e9f3e6187c77","tid":1231343,"uid":210682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"佢同葛佩煩平時喺立法會煩到死"},{"pid":"0a47e8c94bbdb22026b49bf02bd1214cd426ba61","tid":1231343,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:56:53.000Z",